#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizing Toolbars"
msgstr "Prilagajanje orodnih vrstic"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: config.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &gwenview; Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica &gwenview;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: config.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &gwenview; toolbar."
msgstr "Orodna vrstica &gwenview;"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar in <ulink url=\"https://kde.org/applications/graphics/gwenview/"
"\">&gwenview;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica na <ulink url=\"https://apps.kde.org/sl/gwenview/\">&gwenview;"
"</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifying Toolbar Items"
msgstr "Spreminjanje elementov orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To customize an application's toolbars, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"right-click on a toolbar and select <guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</"
"guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prilagoditi orodne vrstice aplikacije, pojdite na "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj orodne "
"vrstice ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali z desno miškino tipko kliknite "
"orodno vrstico in izberite <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj orodne vrstice. ..</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left side of the toolbar configuration panel, the available items "
"that you can put in your toolbar are shown. On the right, the ones that "
"already appear on the toolbar are shown. At the top, you can select the "
"toolbar you wish to modify or view."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani konfiguracijske plošče orodne vrstice so prikazani "
"razpoložljivi elementi, ki jih lahko postavite v orodno vrstico. Na desni "
"strani so prikazani tisti, ki so že prikazani v orodni vrstici. Na vrhu "
"lahko izberete orodno vrstico, ki jo želite spremeniti ali si ogledati."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Above each side of the panel there is a <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> text box "
"you can use to easily find items in the list."
msgstr ""
"Nad vsako stranjo plošče je besedilno polje <guilabel>Filter</guilabel>, ki "
"ga lahko uporabite za preprosto iskanje elementov na seznamu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: config.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Customize Toolbars Window"
msgstr "Okno za prilagajanje orodnih vrstic"

#. Tag: phrase
#: config.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Customize Toolbars window."
msgstr "Okno za prilagajanje orodnih vrstic."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Customize Toolbars window in &gwenview; with the <guibutton>Previous</"
"guibutton> button selected."
msgstr ""
"Okno Prilagodi orodne vrstice v &gwenview; z izbranim gumbom "
"<guibutton>Prejšnji</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding an Item"
msgstr "Dodajanje elementa"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add an item to your toolbar by selecting it from the left side and "
"clicking on the right arrow button."
msgstr ""
"Element lahko dodate v svojo orodno vrstico tako, da ga izberete na levi "
"strani in kliknete gumb s puščico desno."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removing an Item"
msgstr "Odstanjevanje elementa"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can remove an item by selecting it and clicking the left arrow button."
msgstr ""
"Predmet lahko odstranite tako, da ga izberete in kliknete gumb s puščico "
"levo."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing the Position of Items"
msgstr "Spreminjanje položaja elementov"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the position of the items by moving them lower or higher in "
"the list. To move items lower, press the down arrow button, while to move "
"items higher press the up arrow button. You can also change items' position "
"by dragging and dropping them."
msgstr ""
"Položaj elementov lahko spremenite tako, da jih premaknete nižje ali višje "
"na seznamu. Če želite elemente premakniti nižje, pritisnite gumb s puščico "
"navzdol, medtem ko za pomik elementov višje pritisnite gumb s puščico "
"navzgor. Položaj elementov lahko spremenite tudi tako, da jih povlečete in "
"spustite."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On horizontal toolbars, the item that's on top will be the one on the left. "
"On vertical toolbars, items are arranged as they appear in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"V vodoravnih orodnih vrsticah bo element, ki je na vrhu, tisti na levi. V "
"navpičnih orodnih vrsticah so elementi razporejeni tako, kot so prikazani v "
"orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a Separator"
msgstr "Dodajanje ločevalca"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add separator lines between items by adding a <guilabel>--- "
"separator ---</guilabel> item to the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Med elementi lahko dodate ločilne črte tako, da v orodno vrstico dodate "
"element <guilabel>--- ločevalec ---</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restoring Defaults"
msgstr "Obnavljanje privzetih nastavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can restore your toolbar to the way it was when you installed the "
"application by pressing the <guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> button at the "
"bottom of the window and then confirming your decision."
msgstr ""
"Svojo orodno vrstico lahko obnovite na takšno, kot je bila ob namestitvi "
"aplikacije, tako da pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Privzeto</guibutton> na dnu "
"okna in nato potrdite svojo odločitev."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing Text and Icons"
msgstr "Spreminjanje besedila in ikon"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the icon and text of individual toolbar items by selecting an "
"item and clicking either the <guibutton>Change Icon...</guibutton> or "
"<guibutton>Change Text...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ikono in besedilo posameznih elementov orodne vrstice lahko spremenite tako, "
"da izberete element in kliknete gumb <guibutton>Spremeni ikono ...</"
"guibutton> ali <guibutton>Spremeni besedilo ...</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizing Toolbar Appearance"
msgstr "Prilagajanje videza orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the appearance of toolbars by right-clicking on a toolbar to "
"access it's context menu."
msgstr ""
"Videz orodne vrstice lahko spremenite tako, da z desnim klikom na orodno "
"vrstico odprete njen kontekstni meni."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Position"
msgstr "Položaj besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the appearance of text on toolbars in the <guisubmenu>Text "
"Position</guisubmenu> submenu of a toolbar's context menu."
msgstr ""
"Videz besedila v orodnih vrsticah lahko spremenite v podmeniju "
"<guisubmenu>Položaj Besedila</guisubmenu> kontekstnega menija orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:118 config.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can choose from:"
msgstr "Izbirate lahko med:"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Icons</guimenuitem> - only the icon for each toolbar item will "
"appear."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Ikone</guimenuitem> - za vsak element orodne vrstice bo "
"prikazana samo ikona."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Text</guimenuitem> - only the text label for each toolbar item "
"will appear."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Besedilo</guimenuitem> - za vsak element orodne vrstice bo "
"prikazana samo besedilna oznaka."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Text Alongside Icons</guimenuitem> - the text label will appear "
"to the right of each toolbar item's icon"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Besedilo ob ikonah</guimenuitem> - besedilna oznaka bo "
"prikazana desno od ikone vsakega elementa orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Text Under Icons</guimenuitem> - the text label will appear "
"underneath each toolbar item's icon"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Besedilo pod ikonami</guimenuitem> - besedilna oznaka bo "
"prikazana pod ikono vsakega elementa orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also show or hide text for individual toolbar items by right-"
"clicking on an item and checking or unchecking the item under <guilabel>Show "
"Text</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako lahko prikažete ali skrijete besedilo za posamezne elemente orodne "
"vrstice tako, da z desno miškino tipko kliknete element in označite ali "
"počistite element pod <guilabel>Pokaži besedilo</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icon Size"
msgstr "Velikost ikon"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the size of toolbar items' icons by selecting "
"<guisubmenu>Icon Size</guisubmenu> from the toolbar's context menu."
msgstr ""
"Velikost ikon elementov v orodni vrstici lahko spremenite tako, da v "
"kontekstnem meniju orodne vrstice izberete <guisubmenu>Velikost ikon</"
"guisubmenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose from the following options: (each lists the icon size in "
"pixels)"
msgstr ""
"Izbirate lahko med naslednjimi možnostmi: (v vsaki je navedena velikost "
"ikone v slikovnih pikah)"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: config.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "Small (16x16)"
msgstr "Majhna (16x16)"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Medium (22x22)</guimenuitem> [the default value]"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Srednja (22x22)</guimenuitem> [privzeta vrednost]"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: config.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Large (32x32)"
msgstr "Velika (32x32)"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: config.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Huge (48x48)"
msgstr "Ogromna (48x48)"

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving Toolbars"
msgstr "Premikanje orodnih vrstic"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to move toolbars, you must <quote>unlock</quote> them. To do so, "
"uncheck <guimenuitem>Lock Toolbar Positions</guimenuitem> from a toolbar's "
"context menu. To restore the lock, simply recheck this menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite premakniti orodne vrstice, jih morate <quote>odkleniti</quote>. Če "
"želite to narediti, počistite polje <guimenuitem>Zakleni položaje orodne "
"vrstice</guimenuitem> v kontekstnem meniju orodne vrstice. Če jih želite "
"ponovno zakleniti, preprosto znova označite ta element menija."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change a toolbar's position from the <guisubmenu>Orientation</"
"guisubmenu> submenu of its context menu."
msgstr ""
"Položaj orodne vrstice lahko spremenite v podmeniju <guisubmenu>Usmerjenost</"
"guisubmenu> njenega kontekstnega menija."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Top</guimenuitem> [the default in many applications]"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Zgoraj</guimenuitem> [privzeto v mnogih aplikacijah]"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: config.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left"
msgstr "Levo"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: config.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Right"
msgstr "Desno"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: config.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bottom"
msgstr "Spodaj"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also move a toolbar by clicking and holding onto the dotted line at "
"the left of horizontal toolbars or the top of vertical toolbars and dragging "
"it to your desired location."
msgstr ""
"Orodno vrstico lahko premaknete tudi tako, da kliknete in držite pikčasto "
"črto na levi strani vodoravnih orodnih vrstic ali na vrhu navpičnih orodnih "
"vrstic in jo povlečete na želeno mesto."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show/Hide Toolbars"
msgstr "Prikaži/skrij orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your application has only one toolbar, you can hide a toolbar by "
"deselecting <guimenuitem>Show Toolbar</guimenuitem> from either the "
"toolbar's context menu or the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu. To restore "
"the toolbar, select <guimenuitem>Show Toolbar</guimenuitem> from the "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu. Note that toolbars must be "
"<quote>unlocked</quote> to hide them from their context menu; see <xref "
"linkend=\"toolbars-appearance-move\"/> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Če ima vaša aplikacija samo eno orodno vrstico, lahko orodno vrstico "
"skrijete tako, da prekličete izbiro <guimenuitem>Pokaži orodno vrstico</"
"guimenuitem> v kontekstnem meniju orodne vrstice ali v meniju "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu>. Če želite obnoviti orodno vrstico, izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži orodno vrstico</guimenuitem> v meniju "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu>. Upoštevajte, da morajo biti orodne vrstice "
"<quote>odklenjene</quote>, da jih skrijete v kontekstnem meniju; glejte "
"<xref linkend=\"toolbars-appearance-move\"/> za več informacij."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your application has more than one toolbar, a submenu called "
"<guisubmenu>Toolbars Shown</guisubmenu> will appear in the context menu and "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu instead of the above menu entry. From that "
"menu you may select individual toolbars to hide and show."
msgstr ""
"Če ima vaša aplikacija več kot eno orodno vrstico, se namesto zgornjega "
"menijskega vnosa prikaže podmeni z imenom <guisubmenu>Prikazane orodne "
"vrstice</guisubmenu> v kontekstnem meniju in meniju <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu>. V tem meniju lahko izberete posamezne orodne vrstice, ki jih "
"želite skriti ali prikazati."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:214 config.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thanks and Acknowledgments"
msgstr "Zahvale"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Thanks to an anonymous Google Code-In 2011 participant for writing much of "
"this section."
msgstr ""
"Hvala anonimnemu udeležencu Google Code-In 2011 za pisanje večjega dela tega "
"razdelka."

#. Tag: author
#: config.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "<firstname>Alexey</firstname> <surname>Subach</surname>"
msgstr "<firstname>Alexey</firstname> <surname>Subach</surname>"

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using and Customizing Shortcuts"
msgstr "Uporaba in prilagajanje bližnjic"

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many &kde; applications allow you to configure keyboard shortcuts. To open "
"the standard keyboard shortcuts configuration panel, go to "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Veliko &kde; aplikacij vam omogočajo konfiguracijo bližnjic na tipkovnici. "
"Če želite odpreti konfiguracijsko ploščo standardnih bližnjic na tipkovnici, "
"pojdite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the Configure Shortcuts window, you will see a list of all the shortcuts "
"available in the current application. You can use the search box at the top "
"to search for the shortcut you want."
msgstr ""
"V oknu Konfiguriraj bližnjice boste videli seznam vseh bližnjic, ki so na "
"voljo v trenutni aplikaciji. Za iskanje želene bližnjice lahko uporabite "
"iskalno polje na vrhu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: config.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Customize Shortcuts Window"
msgstr "Okno za prilagajanje bližnjic"

#. Tag: phrase
#: config.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Customize Shortcuts window."
msgstr "Okno za prilagajanje bližnjic."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searching for shortcuts with <userinput>file</userinput> in <ulink url="
"\"https://kde.org/applications/system/dolphin/\">&dolphin;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje bližnjic z <userinput>datoteka</userinput> v <ulink url=\"https://"
"kde.org/applications/system/dolphin/\">&dolphin;</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing a Shortcut"
msgstr "Spreminjanje bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change a shortcut, first click on the name of a shortcut you want to "
"change. You will see a radio group where you can choose whether to set the "
"shortcut to its default value, or select a new shortcut for the selected "
"action. To set a new shortcut, choose <guilabel>Custom</guilabel> and click "
"on the button next to it. Then just type the shortcut you would like to use, "
"and your changes will be saved."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti bližnjico, najprej kliknite ime bližnjice, ki jo želite "
"spremeniti. Videli boste izbirno skupino, kjer lahko izberete, ali želite "
"bližnjico nastaviti na privzeto vrednost ali izbrati novo bližnjico za "
"izbrano dejanje. Če želite nastaviti novo bližnjico, izberite <guilabel>Po "
"meri</guilabel> in kliknite gumb poleg nje. Nato samo vnesite bližnjico, ki "
"jo želite uporabiti, in vaše spremembe bodo shranjene."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: config.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting a Shortcut"
msgstr "Nastavitev bližnjice"

#. Tag: phrase
#: config.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Customize Shortcuts window demonstrating how to set a shortcut."
msgstr "Okno Prilagajanje bližnjic, ki prikazuje, kako nastaviti bližnjico."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resetting Shortcuts"
msgstr "Ponastavitev bližnjic "

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is a button at the bottom of the window, called <guibutton>Defaults</"
"guibutton>. Clicking on this button will reset all your custom shortcuts to "
"their default values."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu okna je gumb, imenovan <guibutton>Privzeto</guibutton>. S klikom na "
"ta gumb boste vse vaše bližnjice po meri ponastavili na privzete vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also reset an individual shortcut to its default value by selecting "
"it, and choosing the <guilabel>Default</guilabel> radio button."
msgstr ""
"Posamezno bližnjico lahko tudi ponastavite na privzeto vrednost, tako da jo "
"izberete in izberete izbirni gumb <guilabel>Privzeto</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removing a Shortcut"
msgstr "Odstranitev bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a shortcut, select it from the list, then click the remove icon (a "
"black arrow with a cross) to the right of the button that allows you to "
"select a shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti bližnjico, jo izberite s seznama, nato pa kliknite "
"ikono za odstranitev (črna puščica s križcem) desno od gumba, ki vam omogoča "
"izbiro bližnjice."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Working with Schemes</title>"
msgstr "<title>Delo s shemami</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Schemes are keyboard shortcuts configuration profiles, so you can create "
"several profiles with different shortcuts and switch between these profiles "
"easily."
msgstr ""
"Sheme so konfiguracijski profili bližnjic na tipkovnici, tako da lahko "
"ustvarite več profilov z različnimi bližnjicami in preprosto preklapljate "
"med temi profili."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: config.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Working with Schemes</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Delo s shemami</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: config.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Customize Shortcuts window displaying the scheme editing tools."
msgstr "Okno Prilagajanje bližnjic, ki prikazuje orodja za urejanje sheme."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing a scheme called <userinput>work</userinput>."
msgstr "Urejanje sheme z imenom <userinput>delo</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see a menu allowing you to edit schemes, click on the <guibutton>Manage "
"Schemes</guibutton> button at the bottom of the form. The following options "
"will appear:"
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati meni, ki vam omogoča urejanje shem, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Upravljanje shem</guibutton> na dnu obrazca. Prikazale se bodo "
"naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: config.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Current Scheme"
msgstr "Trenutna shema"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to switch between your schemes."
msgstr "Omogoča preklapljanje med vašimi shemami."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: config.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "New..."
msgstr "Nova..."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new scheme. This opens a window that lets you select a name for "
"your new scheme."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari novo shemo. To odpre okno, v katerem lahko izberete ime za svojo "
"novo shemo."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: config.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Izbriši"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deletes the current scheme."
msgstr "Izbriše trenutno shemo."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: config.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid "More Actions"
msgstr "Več dejanj"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the following menu:"
msgstr "Odpre naslednji meni:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: config.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Shortcuts to scheme"
msgstr "Shrani bližnjice v shemo"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save the current shortcuts to the current scheme."
msgstr "Shrani trenutne bližnjice v trenutno shemo."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: config.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export Scheme..."
msgstr "Izvozi shemo."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exports the current scheme to a file ."
msgstr "Izvozi trenutno shemo kot datoteko."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: config.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import Scheme..."
msgstr "Uvozi shemo..."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Imports a scheme from a file ."
msgstr "Uvozi shemo iz datoteke."

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Printing Shortcuts"
msgstr "Natisni bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can print out a list of shortcuts for easy reference by clicking the "
"<guibutton>Print</guibutton> button at the bottom of the window."
msgstr ""
"Za lažjo uporabo lahko natisnete seznam bližnjic, tako da kliknete gumb "
"<guibutton>Natisni</guibutton> na dnu okna."

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Special thanks to Google Code-In 2011 participant Alexey Subach for writing "
"much of this section."
msgstr ""
"Posebna zahvala udeležencu Google Code-In 2011 Alexeyu Subachu za pisanje "
"večjega dela tega razdelka."
